N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 11.1 - Approved library requirements

State Regulations

The commissioner shall establish regulations for the
registration of libraries and auxiliary units, for personnel, for quarters and
equipment, for collections, for schedules of service and
reports. Notes
